room_title: Escape room "The City of Ashes" by Komnata Quest in New York
room_description: Population: none. You're more than welcome here. You move forward and melt in the fog with the sound of scratching wheels and metal rattling. Long-lasting burnt odor. Anxiety and shudder. You hear the siren scream and forget how to breathe. Welcome to the City of Ashes. Tonight the silence of the city will be broken...
